  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up after a crash on a distant planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a soldier with your friends, beat zombies and magic creatures to find your way home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Softcore and Hardcore modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo play or co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unique character skills customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Open world </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Global and local chat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Friendlist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Seasonal leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Servers in Europe, North America and Asia</p></li></ul>",
